Date: 1999-01-23

Title: On rigid string instantons in four dimensions

Authors: B.G. Konopelchenko, G. Landolfi

Comments: Latex, 7 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B459 (1999) 522-526

Generalized Weierstrass formulae for surfaces in four-dimensional space$\Bbb{R}^{4}$ are used to study (anti)self-dual rigid string configurations. Itis shown that such configurations are given by superminimal immersions into$\Bbb{R}^{4}$. Explicit formulae for generic (anti)instantons are presented.Particular classes of surfaces are also analyzed.